{"tid":1438992,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"伍公子一招道破三毛、分化撚、左膠","createTime":"2019-08-10T03:16:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T03:41:44.000Z","uid":132544,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"201ff62df3ae1f6c0d307d68de0002d6d56e46aa","tid":1438992,"uid":132544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:16:32.000Z","msg":"因社會動盪，港人身心疲憊，鳴金收兵的言論漸已頗有市場。<br />\n<br />\n但見近來愈來愈多勸退廢文，儼然已成實用文體。<br />\n<br />\n以下發佈廢文格式，方便大家參考寫作：<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n範文：<br />\n<br />\n《理性討論》<br />\n<br />\n我肯定和理非與勇武的成效，大家要繼續。<br />\n<br />\n但是，其實大家應該停下來。<br />\n<br />\n因為再進行下去，你們會中計，輿論會轉向。<br />\n<br />\n不要問我，我也沒有答案。<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n寫作要點：<br />\n<br />\n緊記文首説攻，文末説退，如此勸退方能奏效。<br />\n<br />\n最好把撒退說成休息，叫人停下來想一想，可以讓讀者更受落。<br />\n<br />\n強調自己沒有答案，令文章沒有討論空間。<br />\n<br />\n如果想要顯得更有文化氣息，建議在文末加上共勉之。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=3530029770356415&amp;id=203377069688385\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D3530029770356415%26id%3D203377069688385&d=8kP02BZom8b0sC5RUQuyVacrr%2FRj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=b15e610c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=3530029770356415&amp;id=203377069688385</a>"},{"pid":"a95b9f23e99496c3518ef293eef853ad34874c7d","tid":1438992,"uid":132544,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:17:42.000Z","msg":"大家以後見到哩類文體<br />\n<br />\n可以善用不推文功能<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\